"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1928736-Olympics-prize-money-drug-gold-medal\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Team GBicon Jamie Baulch has blasted a drastic change at this year'sOlympics, which sees winning track-and-field athletes given a cash prize for their success in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 170, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 14, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Baulch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jamie Baulch\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Baulch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamie_Baulch\"}, {\"begin\": 164, \"end\": 169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 5.278626407878653e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Athletics supremo Lord Seb Coeannounced that \\u00a340,000 bonuses will go alongside gold medals.\", \"from\": 172, \"to\": 269, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999877613847, \"rank\": 1.2238582127593e-08, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no such rewards for silver or bronze medalists in the French capital, though plans are in motion to do so in time for the LA 2028 Olympics.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 419, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9922482396188478, \"rank\": 0.007442888752385066, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 405, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2028 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2028_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Boxing Association will also reward its gold medal winners with \\u00a377k.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.889704897309481e-12, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the first time since the Games' inception in 1896 that athletes will be paid by a sport's governing body, with former Welsh 400m star Baulch incensed that Coe has decided on financial rewards.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 708, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Baulch has explained that he worries about the potential for rising numbers of drug cheats in the sport, having been awarded his silver medal 13 years late when USA athlete Antonia Pettigrew admitted taking performance-enhancing drugs at the 1997 Games in Atlanta.\", \"from\": 843, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1004, \"end\": 1007, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999948342244083, \"rank\": 4.837675871170502e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1016, \"end\": 1023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonia_Iacobescu\", \"score\": 0.9999999963160917, \"rank\": 3.6295490593444855e-09, \"text\": \"Antonia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonia_Iacobescu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antonia_Iacobescu\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 0.9999999996384759, \"rank\": 3.463756826591217e-10, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He told The Mirror: \\\"Why are you are giving drug cheats a further incentive?\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1185, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been upgraded twice - for the World Championships and then the World Indoors.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Indoors\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Indoor_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I remember I had a lovely presentation to honour my achievement.\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was a hollow feeling - you still feel cheated.\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Roger Black even received his gold medal, which wasn't even a replica version, in the post!\", \"from\": 1392, \"to\": 1483, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.726572255263749e-37, \"text\": \"Roger Black\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Black\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Anyone who takes drugs should never compete again.\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One strike and out.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"End of story.\\\"\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1617, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1618, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1682, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999472493, \"rank\": 5.278626407878653e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1775, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9999883639774779, \"rank\": 1.1622013457712165e-05, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Baulch feels that the prestige of competing, and winning, at the Olympics should trump any financial reward.\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You dream of winning a gold medal - not money,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's the Olympics, the pinnacle for a track and field athlete, but you are putting a price on a gold.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It certainly will not make Dina Asher-Smith for example run any quicker.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2149, \"end\": 2165, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dina Asher-Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dina_Asher-Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lucrative endorsement and sponsorship deals for winning at the Olympics would dwarf the money on offer anyhow.\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I am not sure how well this sits with the athletes from other events.\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be pretty annoyed and it really does not help relations.\", \"from\": 2382, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is what they will be talking about in the camps.\\\"\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2497, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gold medal winners will only be eligible to take home \\u00a340k once they pass the anti-doping procedures, but Baulch recounted a conversation with now-Wales football head coach Craig Bellamy at the London Games that reinforced his position even further.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2672, \"end\": 2685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433879747561203e-24, \"text\": \"Craig Bellamy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2860, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"I remember speaking to Craig Bellamy ahead of London 2012 and he was so excited at competing,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 3103, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3018, \"end\": 3031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.433879747561203e-24, \"text\": \"Craig Bellamy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Craig_Bellamy\"}, {\"begin\": 3041, \"end\": 3052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999548126662, \"rank\": 4.518719024877786e-08, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This was a footballer who had played on the biggest stages.\", \"from\": 3105, \"to\": 3165, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet the prospect of being part of the Olympics was all that mattered to him - not the pay cheque.\\\"\", \"from\": 3166, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3266, \"to\": 3435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3403, \"end\": 3416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1182150633646287e-18, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3452, \"end\": 3465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1182150633646287e-18, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"